@target vue3

The footer of the kun landing page.

layout:
  centered content with:
  - "kun" logo text
  - horizontal links: GitHub (https://github.com/seyyidt/kun-js), npm (https://www.npmjs.com/package/@seyyidt/kun-js), Issues (https://github.com/seyyidt/kun-js/issues)
  - "MIT License" text

constraints:
  - use <script setup lang="ts">
  - scoped styles
  - subtle top border (#262626)
  - muted text colors
  - all external links open in new tab
  - padding top and bottom for breathing room
